ter&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:17px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;=
line-height:150%;text-align:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;"><strong>Steven Cahall</strong>, an equity analy=
st at Wells Fargo,
recently published a comprehensive <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/e=
yJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dUOExWd1VtbThYdW5haWtPZ0QyND0iLCJo=
cmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wdWNrLm5ld3Mvd3AtY29udGVudC91cGxvYWRzLzIwMjQvMTIvV2VsbHM=
tRmFyZ28tTUVESUEtVGhlLTIwMjUtT3JhY2xlLTEyLjE5LjI0LTEucGRmP3V0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj=
1EcnkrUG93ZGVyKy0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MTIlMkYyMiUyRjI0JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX2Nvb=
